-container\">\n<h2>2. Koh Tao Viewpoints<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Viewpoints can make you speechless, and that feeling&#xA0;is great. Koh Tao has a lot of these viewpoints if you compare it to the size of the small island. All of the viewpoints are on private property so for some there&#x2019;s a small entrance fee.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also see:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/koh-lipe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Koh Lipe, Thailand&#x2019;s Paradise Island<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Mango Viewpoint<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At this beautiful viewpoint, you&#x2019;ll have a view of Sairee Beach and Mae Haad Bay that stretches all the way to the south. The way up is not the easiest, so make sure you&#x2019;re wearing comfortable shoes unless you&#x2019;re that flip-flop kind of person. The entrance fee for Mango Viewpoint is 100 THB.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/koh-tao\/chumphon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find boat times and tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<div><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view.jpg\" alt=\"thailand koh tao mango viewpoint view\"><\/noscript><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1094 size-full lazypreload\" alt=\"thailand koh tao mango viewpoint view\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-tao-mango-viewpoint-view-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165248\/thailand-koh-t