group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Motorbike rental Koh Tao<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Motorbikes can be rented&#xA0;for an average price of 200TBH a day. Be careful about giving your passport because sadly motorbike scams are a thing on this island. We can highly recommend&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.com\/Attraction_Review-g303910-d7024182-Reviews-Oli_s_Motorbike_Rentals-Koh_Tao_Surat_Thani_Province.html\">Oli&#x2019;s Motorbike Rentals<\/a>&#xA0;and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.com\/Attraction_Review-g303910-d4039865-Reviews-RPM_Koh_Tao-Koh_Tao_Surat_Thani_Province.html\">RPM<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees.jpg\" alt=\"thailand koh tao to do john suwan viewpoint\"><\/noscript><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1099 size-full lazypreload\" alt=\"thailand koh tao to do john suwan viewpoint\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165236\/thailand-koh-tao-john-suwan-viewpoint-palmtrees-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com