ree beach sunset paddleboarding\"><\/noscript><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1085 size-large lazypreload\" alt=\"thailand koh tao to do sairee beach sunset paddleboarding\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunset-paddleboarding-1440x1080.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165309\/thailand-koh-tao-sairee-beach-sunse